stateDiagram-v2
    direction LR
    [*] --> draft: Job 3 自动创建\n(每月5号)
    draft --> draft: Ops 使用 Auto-fill\n或 Add/Delete Item
    draft --> pending_approval: Ops 提交审核
    pending_approval --> approved: Finance 审批通过
    pending_approval --> rejected: Finance 驳回
    rejected --> draft: 退回修改

    classDef auto fill:#E8F5E9,stroke:#4CAF50,stroke-width:2px
    classDef ops fill:#E3F2FD,stroke:#2196F3,stroke-width:2px
    classDef finance fill:#F3E5F5,stroke:#9C27B0,stroke-width:2px
    classDef rejected fill:#FFEBEE,stroke:#F44336,stroke-width:2px

    class draft auto
    class pending_approval ops
    class approved finance
    class rejected rejected
